                    </div>
                    <h3>Web Maintenance</h3>
                    <p>Regular updates, security checks, and performance optimization to keep your website running smoothly.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service-card">
                    <div class="service-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-server"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>API Integration</h3>
                    <p>Connecting your website with third-party services through API integration for enhanced functionality.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
